      "action": "Minh runs into the bright art classroom, stops, and waves excitedly at the camera. with other students visible in the background",
      "camera_movement": "Wide shot, static, then medium shot on Minh",
      "dialogue": "Hi! I'm Minh! Today I'm going to show you my FAVORITE class \u00e2\u0080\u0094 Art!",
      "mood": "Joyful and energetic",
      "veo_prompt": "Pixar-style 3D animation, wide shot establishing a bright school art classroom with colorful drawings on walls, a 6-year-old Vietnamese boy with short black hair and a light blue school uniform runs into the center, stops, and waves with a huge grin, warm morning sunlight, 8 seconds, with diverse 6-year-old students sitting at desks and busy with art projects in the background",
      "dialogue_vn": "Ch\u00c3\u00a0o c\u00c3\u00a1c b\u00e1\u00ba\u00a1n! M\u00c3\u00acnh l\u00c3\u00a0 Minh! H\u00c3\u00b4m nay m\u00c3\u00acnh s\u00e1\u00ba\u00bd gi\u00e1\u00bb\u009bi thi\u00e1\u00bb\u0087u cho c\u00c3\u00a1c b\u00e1\u00ba\u00a1n ti\u00e1\u00ba\u00bft h\u00e1\u00bb\u008dc Y\u00c3\u008aU TH\u00c3\u008dCH nh\u00e1\u00ba\u00a5t c\u00e1\u00bb\u00a7a m\u00c3\u00acnh \u00e2\u0080\u0094 M\u00e1\u00bb\u00b9 thu\u00e1\u00ba\u00adt!"
    },
    {
