      "characters": [
        "char_001"
      ],
      "background": "bg_001",
      "action": "Minh spins around with arms wide, then holds up a finger knowingly. with other students visible in the background",
      "camera_movement": "Medium shot, slow tracking as he spins",
      "dialogue": "In art class, we learn about something really cool\u00e2\u0080\u00a6 called ART PRODUCTS!",
      "mood": "Enthusiastic and mysterious",
      "veo_prompt": "Pixar-style 3D animation, medium shot of a 6-year-old Vietnamese boy in a blue uniform spinning joyfully with arms wide in a colorful classroom, he stops and holds up one finger with a playful, knowing expression, bright and cheerful atmosphere, 8 seconds, with diverse 6-year-old students sitting at desks and busy with art projects in the background",
      "dialogue_vn": "Trong gi\u00e1\u00bb\u009d m\u00e1\u00bb\u00b9 thu\u00e1\u00ba\u00adt, ch\u00c3\u00bang m\u00c3\u00acnh \u00c4\u0091\u00c6\u00b0\u00e1\u00bb\u00a3c h\u00e1\u00bb\u008dc v\u00e1\u00bb\u0081 m\u00e1\u00bb\u0099t \u00c4\u0091i\u00e1\u00bb\u0081u c\u00e1\u00bb\u00b1c k\u00e1\u00bb\u00b3 th\u00c3\u00ba v\u00e1\u00bb\u008b... \u00c4\u0091\u00c3\u00b3 l\u00c3\u00a0 S\u00e1\u00ba\u00a2N PH\u00e1\u00ba\u00a8M M\u00e1\u00bb\u00b8 THU\u00e1\u00ba\u00acT!"
    },
