      "background": "bg_001",
      "action": "Minh explains visual art, pointing to a clay bird on a shelf. with other students visible in the background",
      "camera_movement": "Close-up on Minh, then pan to the clay bird",
      "dialogue": "Visual Art means\u00e2\u0080\u00a6 things we make that you LOOK at. Like paintings. And drawings. And \u00e2\u0080\u0094 sculptures!",
      "mood": "Instructive and happy",
      "veo_prompt": "Pixar-style 3D animation, close-up of a cheerful 6-year-old boy talking and gesturing, camera pans to show a small clay bird sculpture on a wooden shelf in a sunlit classroom, vibrant colors, clear and detailed rendering, 8 seconds, with diverse 6-year-old students sitting at desks and busy with art projects in the background",
      "dialogue_vn": "M\u00e1\u00bb\u00b9 thu\u00e1\u00ba\u00adt t\u00e1\u00ba\u00a1o h\u00c3\u00acnh ngh\u00c4\u00a9a l\u00c3\u00a0... nh\u00e1\u00bb\u00afng th\u00e1\u00bb\u00a9 ch\u00c3\u00bang m\u00c3\u00acnh l\u00c3\u00a0m ra \u00c4\u0091\u00e1\u00bb\u0083 c\u00c3\u00a1c b\u00e1\u00ba\u00a1n NG\u00e1\u00ba\u00aeM nh\u00c3\u00acn. Nh\u00c6\u00b0 tranh v\u00e1\u00ba\u00bd n\u00c3\u00a0y, h\u00c3\u00acnh v\u00e1\u00ba\u00bd n\u00c3\u00a0y, v\u00c3\u00a0 c\u00e1\u00ba\u00a3 \u00e2\u0080\u0094 nh\u00e1\u00bb\u00afng b\u00e1\u00bb\u00a9c t\u00c6\u00b0\u00e1\u00bb\u00a3ng n\u00e1\u00bb\u00afa!"
    },
